    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Compositions of tunes, melodies, or other pieces of music or song in which a single melodic line predominates, and which has little or no distinctive accompaniment; if a song, may have simple or unobtrusive accompaniment.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
